<h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zeniaRosaOscuro pt-2">INTRALIPOTHERAPY</h3>
<p><strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">Intralipotherapy</strong> is one of the most innovative techniques for <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">eliminating localised fat</strong>. A deoxycholic acid solution is injected causing <strong class="font-bold underline text-zeniaRosaOscuro">fat to be destroyed and liquefied</strong>, dissolving adipocytes.</p>`,
